About Rainbow Six Siege X:
Rainbow Six Siege X is an exciting, new approach to the first-person shooter experience that puts tactical combat and masterful destruction at the center of the action. Lead your team of unique operators through tense and thrilling combat scenarios, and achieve victory through smart preparation and strategic improvisation. Rainbow Six Siege X is available now on Xbox, PlayStation® and PC.

description:
The countdown is on. Only 21 days until TOM CLANCY'S SPLINTER CELL: DEATHWATCH, a new animated series based on the acclaimed Ubisoft video game series.

From Derek Kolstad, the writer behind the John Wick franchise, comes the first-ever adaptation of the acclaimed stealth video game franchise, Tom Clancy’s Splinter Cell. After a long absence from the field, legendary agent Sam Fisher (Liev Schreiber) is drawn back into action when a wounded young operative (Kirby Howell-Baptiste) seeks his help. TOM CLANCY'S SPLINTER CELL: DEATHWATCH will be available worldwide on October 14 on Netflix.

About Ubisoft Film & Television

Ubisoft Film & Television’s mission is to bring Ubisoft’s award-winning games into new areas of entertainment and to create original stories set in the world, culture, and community of gaming. description:
"Eywa has abandoned you." 

So’lek’s journey begins in fire and vengeance. Prepare for the next chapter in Avatar: Frontiers of Pandora - From the Ashes, coming 19 December 2025.

About Avatar: Frontiers of Pandora - From the Ashes:
Set after the events of the first Avatar film, you’ll embark on a journey across the Western Frontier, a never-before-seen continent of Pandora, as you join other Na’vi clans to protect Pandora from the formidable forces of the RDA. Created in collaboration with Lightstorm Entertainment and Disney, you will experience a first-person open-world action-adventure game exclusively developed to maximize the power of new-gen consoles and PC. 

Continue your adventure in the Western frontier in the all new From the Ashes expansion. Follow So'lek's journey against a ruthless and unexpected enemy. 

#Ubisoft #AvatarFrontiers
title: Avatar: Frontiers of Pandora – From the Ashes: EXPANSION REVEAL TEASER
